{
  "levelId": "block-06",
  "chapterId": "block-06",
  "worldId": "block",
  "title": "地下城星门：唤醒回家门",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 8
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "gate",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/block/block-06.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "星门晶石放进地下城中央，三张地图的光一起聚拢。科幻、森林和方块世界终于连成了一条路。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是地下城星门。我们先把“唤醒回家门”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到方块碰撞的声音，新的建造点就在前面。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先找稳固的方块，再一步一步搭出安全的路线。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "care",
          "prompt": "给星门放上最后一颗温暖的伙伴之心。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "放上伙伴之心",
              "feedback": "星门亮起柔和的光，欢迎大家回家。"
            },
            {
              "label": "和朋友击掌",
              "feedback": "击掌的声音变成星光，飞向三张地图。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，放上伙伴之心让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "方块放稳后，藏在墙后的通道露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这段通道接到村子的道路上，伙伴们就能一起通过。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这块特别的方块，它会成为下一座建筑的起点。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "今天的故事结束了，下一次打开地图，还会有新的路。",
          "character": "narrator",
          "position": "center"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
          "hero",
          "pet"
        ],
